{"tid":2479160,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李靜儀Heidi玩滾軸溜冰晒好身材！ 烏身谷出小山丘一洗iPad之名","createTime":"2021-04-07T15:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T15:21:15.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a840e22ac9a6ebebd441e2d194ed07a4c052633d","tid":2479160,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:14:04.000Z","msg":"近幾日天氣雖然又涼番小小，但依然無阻一眾女士開始晒身材，而近日女子組合 Super Girls 成員李靜儀（Heidi）就喺社交網上傳咗佢去玩滾軸溜冰嘅相同片，表現仲相當專業添！<br />\n<br />\nSuper Girls 嘅李靜儀最近就愛上咗玩滾軸溜冰，佢喺 IG 上傳咗佢喺街場大顯身手嘅相同片，片中見佢著上小背心同貼身運動褲，喺做足安全措施下施展渾身解數，表現得相當自在！<br />\n<br />\n而喺片中佢仲烏身大晒事業線，雖然佢一直都被指 iPad 胸，但睇番依條片，見佢身材唔止好咗，仲擠出咗小山丘派福利，疑似升級咗添喎！<br />\n<br />\n不過睇佢玩得咁輕鬆自在，完全睇唔出佢上一次玩已經係 20 年前嘅事喇，佢笑言：「每次跌倒 都是為了再次爬起 忌水 怕水 而且唔識游水 都係學返陸地上既運動岩我 十歲後就無再玩過 今年要認真搵呀sir 補鐘」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZySRP0W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZySRP0W.jpg&h=3e1283ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YoNB07C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYoNB07C.jpg&h=27a7a183&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/joDEYUi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjoDEYUi.jpg&h=04cdc508&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0796db0974822fdf5cade48c5535346398a99a87","tid":2479160,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:15:46.000Z","msg":"那麼醜的女！"},{"pid":"f2682a57f0f927ca9f9a8b07a281b1846898e3c7","tid":2479160,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:16:12.000Z","msg":"罩仲大過波<br />\n<img src=\"https://67.media.tumblr.com/95826769fc9f31ff1de36494f7cd8409/tumblr_oddgnd8cXd1vaittto1_540.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F67.media.tumblr.com%2F95826769fc9f31ff1de36494f7cd8409%2Ftumblr_oddgnd8cXd1vaittto1_540.gif&h=071864e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b2d776e3a813a3df5c2ee8d6d58740d54e6c699","tid":2479160,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike"